<h1 id="propuestas-de-proyecto">Propuestas de Proyecto</h1>

<h2 id="clairvoyants-and-mirrors">1: Clairvoyants and Mirrors</h2>

<h3 id="descripcin-general">Descripción general</h3>
<p>Grift everyone by pretending to be a clairvoyant! A parody game about new age pseudo-cults, andrew tate and redpill movements</p>

<h3 id="mecnicas">Mecánicas</h3>
<p>Suck dry your clients wallets by distributing your huuuge amount of brains, knowledge, and smarts. Earn all the money in the world, morals be darned! Use manipulation tactics to instill loyalty on those poor, desperate, people; and get your way to the top of the promised Man-adise, and leave no brain unwashed (hygene is important, after all!)</p>

<h3 id="gameplay">Gameplay</h3>
